Revision history for Task-Sites-ShlomiFish:

0.0209  2014-01-31
        - Add separate LICENSE file (CPANTS).
        - Explicit 'mit' license in Build.PL / META.yml.
        - Minimal perl version (CPANTS).
        - Add t/cpan-changes.t , t/pod-coverage.t , t/pod.t
        and t/style-trailing-space.t .

0.0208  2013-05-11
        - Add more dependencies.
        - Convert to Build.PL / Module-Build to handle three version
        digits properly.

0.0207  2012-03-24
        - Add DBD::SQLite (it is needed).
        - Add JSON.

0.0206  2011-06-09
        - Add HTML::TreeBuilder::LibXML .
        - Add XML::Amazon .
        - Add Imager .

0.0205  2011-06-07
        - Made the XML::Grammar::Fiction and XML::Grammar::Screenplay versions
        0.7.0.
        - Add many more explicit and implicit used or required modules.

0.0204  2010-12-15
        - Add Term::ReadPassword.

0.0203  2010-10-16
        - Add Spork::Shlomify , Text::VimColor and XML::Grammar::Fiction
        that are now needed to build the site.
        - Remove WWW::Google::SiteMap - no longer needed.
        - Add the tag-release.pl file to tag a release using Subversion.

0.0202  2009-03-04
        - Added more dependencies: App::XML::DocBook::Builder ,
        String::ShellQuote, and the XML::Grammar's.
            - These are now required by the module.
        - Revised the POD in lib/Task/Sites/ShlomiFish.pm to make the
        intentions that this is a task for publically-available source
        code clearer.
        - Added the NOTE about the motivation to the POD.

0.0201  2006-09-10
        - Added XML::Grammar::ProductsSyndication that is required for
        the music syndication (and future syndications).
        - Added XML::LibXML::XPathContext.

0.0100  2006-06-15
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

